						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in front of Hazrat Teg Burhanuddin Dargh-(1).</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1310 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It states that Gaṅgidēva rāṇeya made a gift of land for the maintenance of a <hi rend="italic">dharma-ēta</hi> (charitable Picotta).</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1232 Sādhāraṇa corresponding to 1310 A.D.</p>						

